title: Navy Accepts Delivery of Future USS Milwaukee (LCS 5) (The United States Navy)
text: ( Source : The United States Navy ) MARINETTE, Wis ( NNS ) -- The U.S. Navy accepted delivery of the future USS Milwaukee ( LCS 5) during a ceremony at the Marinette Marine Corporation shipyard Oct. 16. Milwaukee is the sixth littoral combat ship
